Package org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.alt.twoway

Class Summary
AbstractTwoWayAltAutomatonCreator This is an abstract creator for creating two-way alternating automata with propositional alphabet and labels on transitions.
CNFNTWABWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating Büchi word automaton (NTWABW) in CNF form.
CNFNTWACWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating co-Büchi word automaton (NTWACW) in CNF form.
CNFNTWAGBWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating generalized Büchi word automaton (NTWAGBW) in CNF form.
CNFNTWAMWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating Muller word automaton (NTWAMW) in CNF form.
CNFNTWAPWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating parity word automaton (NTWAPW) in CNF form.
CNFNTWARWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating Rabin word automaton (NTWARW) in CNF form.
CNFNTWASWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating Streett word automaton (NTWASW) in CNF form.
DNFNTWABWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating Büchi word automaton (NTWABW) in DNF form.
DNFNTWACWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating co-Büchi word automaton (NTWACW) in DNF form.
DNFNTWAGBWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating generalized Büchi word automaton (NTWAGBW) in DNF form.
DNFNTWAMWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating Muller word automaton (NTWAMW) in DNF form.
DNFNTWAPWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating parity word automaton (NTWAPW) in DNF form.
DNFNTWARWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating Rabin word automaton (NTWARW) in DNF form.
DNFNTWASWCreator This is a creator that can create a nondeterministic two-way alternating Streett word automaton (NTWASW) in DNF form.
TwoWayAltAutomaton A TwoWayAltAutomaton is a nondeterministic alternating automaton with two directions on transitions.
TwoWayAltTransition A TwoWayAltTransition is an alternating transition with a forward or backward direction.
TwoWaySuccessor A two-way successor contains a set of backward successors and a set of forward successors.
 

Enum Summary
Direction This class defines the direction of a transition in a two-way alternating automaton.
